## Process commands

For harnesses without a native command menu: invoke a phase by reading the
section named below.

- **brainstorm** — idea → approved design (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Brainstorm)
- **plan** — design → zero-context task plan (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Plan)
- **execute** — build the plan test-driven (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Execute)
- **review** — the merge gate, depth by tier (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Review)
- **quick** — Tier 1–2 shortcut (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Quick)
- **debug** — root-cause before fixing (`docs/process/workflow.md`, Debug)
- **commit** — one atomic conventional commit (`docs/process/commits.md`)
- **prime** — restore working context (`docs/process/journal-state-plans.md`)
